5. Cost Breakdown Structure (CBS)

5.1 Purpose

CBS is the authoritative financial decomposition framework.

No cost may exist outside the CBS.

Every cost object shall reference a CBS node.

⸻

5.2 Governance Principles

* Every dollar has a CBS identifier.
* Every CBS node is auditable.
* Every CBS node is event sourced.
* Every CBS node supports dependency analysis.
* Every CBS node supports RTM linkage.
* Every CBS node supports automated roll-ups.

