10. Event Sourcing

All financial state shall derive from immutable events.

Supported event types:

* cost_created
* cost_updated
* cost_deleted
* cbs_node_created
* cbs_node_updated
* vendor_quote_received
* forecast_updated
* contingency_adjusted
* procurement_awarded

Current state must always be reconstructable from event history.

⸻

11. Contingency Governance

Contingency shall be explicit.

Contingency may not be:

* hidden
* embedded
* inferred

Contingency shall exist as dedicated CBS nodes.

