16. CBS Validation Rules

Critical rules:

CBS_RULE_001

Every cost object references a valid CBS node.

CBS_RULE_002

No orphan CBS nodes.

CBS_RULE_003

Parent CBS node must exist before child creation.

CBS_RULE_004

CBS hierarchy encoding must remain valid.

CBS_RULE_005

subtotal = quantity × unit_cost

CBS_RULE_006

Confidence score mandatory.

CBS_RULE_007

Manual roll-up totals prohibited.

CBS_RULE_008

RFQ → RTM → CBS traceability mandatory.

